            </mods:physicalDescription>
            <mods:note type="Content">Istomin and his guests share opinions on twentieth-century pianists who returned to the Urtext as a basis for interpretation as well views on those who exercise an excess of bodily motion in performance.</mods:note>
          </mods:relatedItem>
