              <mods:form>video</mods:form>
              <mods:reformattingQuality>access</mods:reformattingQuality>
              <mods:extent>3:02</mods:extent>
              <mods:digitalOrigin>reformatted digital</mods:digitalOrigin>
            </mods:physicalDescription>
            <mods:note type="Content">Istomin provides an epilogue to the discussions by paying homage to other great pianists, including Ignace Paderweski, Artur Schnabel, Rudolf Serkin, Claudio Arrau, and Dame Myra Hess.</mods:note>
